019s just one of the many great games Arkane has made, all of which are worth\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/steam-arkane-sale-dishonored-deathloop-prey-pc-1851678706\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1370795, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/steam-arkane-sale-dishonored-deathloop-prey-pc-1851678706", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/c6dc3370f66936d0d452e988cc7f3710.jpg", "title": "Arkane\u2019s Amazing Library Of Immersive Sims Gets Big Discount On Steam", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-22T18:45:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f88bf326b1894a17bd0a3e09f6d698c8.jpg\"/><p>Marvel\u2019s Blade, first announced in 2019, has once again been delayed. The reboot of the franchise that is set to bring the daywalker and vampire killer into the Marvel Cinematic Universe was set to arrive in 2025, but now doesn\u2019t have a release date. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-blade-reboot-delay-production-issues-2025-mcu-1851678580\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1370420, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/marvel-blade-reboot-delay-production-issues-2025-mcu-1851678580", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f88bf326b1894a17bd0a3e09f6d698c8.jpg", "title": "Marvel's Blade Reboot Delayed Again As It Loses 2025 Release Window", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "alb